Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.86,0:00:14.89,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:15.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:18.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:23.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:26.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:30.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:34.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:36.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:40.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:45.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:51.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:54.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:59.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:03.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:13.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:15.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:18.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:24.82,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fs175\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,160.389)}Showdown!! Snowy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:24.82,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs130\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,690.389)}Mountain Monster Bearkonger
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Pops and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, they're over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.85,0:01:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:01:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This mountain's gonna end\Nup with a bunch of holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's have another run.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I appreciate Pops\Nmaking time for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one time we\Ncan be grateful to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right! \N- Well, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato and Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a nice rest, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure nothing will\Nhappen to interrupt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,\Nwhat's wrong with you girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a load of these lazy\Ngirls, Mr. Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can\Nski any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going, okay? Just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, ski! Ski!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing and go after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you expect?\NHe is a beginner, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- Was it around here?\N- Where could it have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was more this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be\Nsomewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a child-sized ski?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It slid into the\Nunderbrush there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman, I'll go find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous!\NDon't go in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go in where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's ravine under that snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just this year, more than ten\Npeople have fallen and gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, son!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Goro. Say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be my friend in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Friend? Sounds good to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.36,0:04:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tadashi Mikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ishikura Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is Mika and\NEmi, Tobei, and Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tadashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you how to ski\Ntomorrow, Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine o'clock tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine o'clock? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That blasted,\Ninterfering Mikawa child...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.42,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\3c&H0B4397&}Hotel Village
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"We're here at the Hotel Village\Nat the Kusatsu Highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very nice place."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That awful card again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me feel so uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's turned into a blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doctor Mikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doctor Mikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:23.38,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs60\3c&H264779&}Mikawa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Operation:\NSnow proceeding?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It will soon be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:42.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Operation: Snow is Shocker's plan to\Nmelt the snow in the Kusatsu Highlands
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:45.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and cause massive flooding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:49.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To accomplish this, Shocker has\Nthreatened physicist Doctor Saburo Mikawa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:51.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,into creating energy bombs that\Ncan generate 2000 degrees of heat
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:54.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,for an extended period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:07:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen,\Nwe must speed up the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bearkonger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your job is to keep\Nobstacles out of our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow Mikawa's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you call me\Nout at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Mikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son has made friends with\Nsome truly dire characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato,\Nof all people...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I made your energy bombs so\Nthat you'd spare my son's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done enough, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't harm Tadashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If your son learns our secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,we will kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I will provide a demonstration.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, watch carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't wish to see\Nyour son die like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,keep him away from\NIchimonji and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you understand,\Nthen you may go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it be? Was Tadashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tadashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tadashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't see us anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...\Nafter I said we could be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tadashi,\Ncould you please tell us why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll kill me if I tell\Nyou, Mr. Ichimonji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Bearkonger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch Tadashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw him in a cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa! Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take him away!\N- Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, you go for Tadashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finished now, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't over, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:44.22,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You great fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't even\Nkill one child?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Bearkonger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You must do what it takes to lure\Nout Ichimonji and his allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear upon my life\Nthat I will succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Arm the energy bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty minutes to detonation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So your father was forced\Nto work with Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But to melt the snow in the Kusatsu\NHighlands to cause major flooding...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like\Nsomething they'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ichimonji,\Nplease save my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The incinerator at our house...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a terrible fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.\NMy body can take worse than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, they'll probably\Ntry to strike elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi and Mika have been\Ngone a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:16.70,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs60\3c&H0B4397&}Hotel Village
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.35,0:15:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Go help cool him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That will do you no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Mika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That was scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is room 412, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You should check a room's\Nnumber before you enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NSomething's wrong here, Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,412... this is our room!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounded like Mika and Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ichimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you? Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look up on that hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They never give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Bearkonger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops! Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy bombs will\Ngo off in five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry... go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better hurry.\NWe only have five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, you handle things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What now, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:21:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tadashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.61,0:22:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't thank you all\Nenough for what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.30,0:22:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.32,0:22:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to thank us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Mr. Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we're\Nfriends with Tadashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.22,0:22:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't we spend\Nanother couple days here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.28,0:22:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in Kusatsu, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A bath in the hot springs will\Nheal our wounds in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.98,0:22:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.48,0:22:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.18,0:22:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm gonna go for a swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go put our\Nbathing suits on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.99,0:22:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna swim, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.62,0:22:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Kusatsu's water\Nwas good for injuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but does that go for\Nthe heated pool, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a psychological thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:22:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My wounds are all healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.74,0:22:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we hit\Nthe slopes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.12,0:23:02.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider had put a stop\Nto Shocker's evil plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:05.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But as long as evil exists in this\Nworld, the Kamen Rider will fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.82,0:23:07.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For the sake of\Npeace and justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:10.59,Cont,,0,70,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:13.68,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:16.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.34,0:23:18.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the ice devil Todogiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.02,0:23:23.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The evil Shocker uses the devil Todogiller\Nin their plan to freeze all of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.54,0:23:25.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:28.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Deadly Ice\NDevil Todogiller."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.19,0:23:30.74,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,200.389)}The Deadly Ice Devil
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.19,0:23:30.74,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs215\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,740.389)}Todogiller
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:40.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.85,0:23:42.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:44.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.81,0:23:47.86,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:50.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.23,0:23:52.11,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.11,0:23:53.90,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.90,0:23:55.35,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.70,0:23:57.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:03.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:07.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.04,0:24:10.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.14,0:24:15.55,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Showdown!!\NSnowy Mountain Monster Bearkonger
Comment: 0,0:23:28.19,0:23:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Deadly Ice Devil Todogiller